  "description": "Khene in the subterranean register — heavy filter, maximum buzz, full paired-pipe beating at low frequencies. The detuned pipe pairs at 1.000/1.003 produce a slow 0.14 Hz beating at A1 (55 Hz), which is not vibrato but physical weight. A drone that doesn't so much play as arrive. Play low. Hold long. Let the crosstalk blur the voices.",
